{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-18",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_18_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Fall Guy",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 8,
  "page_start_sec": 501.72,
  "page_end_sec": 745.36,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.553,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 501.72,
      "end": 502.32,
      "text": "\"Well, sir, I grant you that's one way of doing it, but—\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 502.34,
      "end": 502.58,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.74,
      "end": 505.3,
      "text": "I grant you that's one way of doing it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 505.32,
      "end": 505.97,
      "text": "but..."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.8,
      "end": 507.16,
      "text": "\"'But' hell!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 507.4,
      "end": 508.06,
      "text": "Spade said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 508.26,
      "end": 509.58,
      "text": "\"It's the only way.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 509.8,
      "end": 513.3,
      "text": "His eyes were hot and earnest under a reddening forehead."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.92,
      "end": 515.76,
      "text": "The bruise on his temple was liver-colored."
    },
    {
      "start": 516.48,
      "end": 517.9,
      "text": "I know what I'm talking about."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.29,
      "end": 519.2,
      "text": "I've been through"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.2,
      "end": 521.38,
      "text": "it all before and expect to go through it again."
    },
    {
      "start": 522.18,
      "end": 523.2,
      "text": "At one time or another,"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.42,
      "end": 524.74,
      "text": "I've had to tell everybody"
    },
    {
      "start": 524.74,
      "end": 527.0,
      "text": "from the Supreme Court down to go to hell,"
    },
    {
      "start": 527.4,
      "end": 528.56,
      "text": "and I've got away with it."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.76,
      "end": 530.3,
      "text": "I got away with it because"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.42,
      "end": 533.72,
      "text": "I never let myself forget that a day of reckoning was coming."
    },
    {
      "start": 534.24,
      "end": 536.32,
      "text": "I never forget that when the day of"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.42,
      "end": 536.98,
      "text": "reckoning comes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.6,
      "end": 539.72,
      "text": "I want to be all set to march into headquarters,"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.04,
      "end": 541.4,
      "text": "pushing a victim in front of me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.52,
      "end": 541.78,
      "text": "saying,"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.3,
      "end": 544.2,
      "text": "'Here, you chumps, is your criminal.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 545.16,
      "end": 546.28,
      "text": "As long as I can do that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.34,
      "end": 547.88,
      "text": "I can put my thumb to my nose"
    },
    {
      "start": 547.88,
      "end": 550.5,
      "text": "and wriggle my fingers at all the laws in the book."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.74,
      "end": 552.42,
      "text": "The first time I can't do it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.46,
      "end": 553.38,
      "text": "my name's mud."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.06,
      "end": 555.64,
      "text": "There hasn't been a first time yet."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.12,
      "end": 557.14,
      "text": "This isn't going to be it."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.28,
      "end": 558.18,
      "text": "That's flat."
    },
    {
      "start": 559.424,
      "end": 560.44,
      "text": "Gutman's eyes flickered",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 560.88,
      "end": 562.42,
      "text": "and their sleekness became dubious,"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.94,
      "end": 565.54,
      "text": "but he held his other features in their bulbous pink smiling"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.08,
      "end": 566.66,
      "text": "complacent cast,"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.86,
      "end": 569.52,
      "text": "and there was nothing of uneasiness in his voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 570.36,
      "end": 570.74,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.98,
      "end": 572.38,
      "text": "that's a system that's got"
    },
    {
      "start": 572.38,
      "end": 573.82,
      "text": "a lot to recommend it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 573.92,
      "end": 574.12,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.24,
      "end": 575.5,
      "text": "by Gad, it has!"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.32,
      "end": 578.6,
      "text": "And if it was anyway practical this time,"
    },
    {
      "start": 578.8,
      "end": 579.48,
      "text": "I'd be the"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.56,
      "end": 580.22,
      "text": "first to say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.34,
      "end": 581.82,
      "text": "stick to it by all means,"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.96,
      "end": 582.22,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.06,
      "end": 585.36,
      "text": "But this just happens to be a case where it's not"
    },
    {
      "start": 585.48,
      "end": 585.88,
      "text": "possible."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.29,
      "end": 588.96,
      "text": "That's the way it is with the best of systems."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.88,
      "end": 591.3,
      "text": "There comes a time when you've got to"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.42,
      "end": 591.96,
      "text": "make exceptions,"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.18,
      "end": 594.62,
      "text": "and a wise man just goes ahead and makes them."
    },
    {
      "start": 595.16,
      "end": 595.42,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.46,
      "end": 595.68,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.84,
      "end": 597.2,
      "text": "that's just the way it"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.2,
      "end": 598.04,
      "text": "is in this case,"
    },
    {
      "start": 598.44,
      "end": 600.14,
      "text": "and I don't mind telling you that I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.14,
      "end": 602.26,
      "text": "you're being very well paid for making an"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.32,
      "end": 602.62,
      "text": "exception."
    },
    {
      "start": 603.78,
      "end": 605.54,
      "text": "Now maybe it will be a little more trouble"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.54,
      "end": 607.64,
      "text": "to you than if you had your victim to"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.64,
      "end": 608.8,
      "text": "hand over to the police,"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.98,
      "end": 609.08,
      "text": "but,"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.64,
      "end": 611.36,
      "text": "he laughed and spread his hands—"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.83,
      "end": 613.76,
      "text": "you're not a man that's afraid of a"
    },
    {
      "start": 613.76,
      "end": 614.5,
      "text": "little bit of trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.92,
      "end": 616.66,
      "text": "You know how to do things,"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.0,
      "end": 619.24,
      "text": "and you know you'll land on your feet in the end,"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.52,
      "end": 620.56,
      "text": "no matter what happens."
    },
    {
      "start": 621.24,
      "end": 623.48,
      "text": "He pursed his lips and partly closed one eye."
    },
    {
      "start": 623.72,
      "end": 624.86,
      "text": "You'll manage that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.02,
      "end": 625.28,
      "text": "sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 626.56,
      "end": 628.1,
      "text": "Spade's eyes had lost their warmth.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 628.3,
      "end": 630.3,
      "text": "His face was dull and lumpy."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.58,
      "end": 632.24,
      "text": "I know what I'm talking about,"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.42,
      "end": 633.4,
      "text": "he said in a low,"
    },
    {
      "start": 633.54,
      "end": 635.1,
      "text": "consciously patient tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.53,
      "end": 637.46,
      "text": "This is my city and my game."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.34,
      "end": 639.44,
      "text": "I could manage to land"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.52,
      "end": 640.16,
      "text": "on my feet,"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.24,
      "end": 640.6,
      "text": "sure,"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.76,
      "end": 641.3,
      "text": "this time."
    },
    {
      "start": 641.92,
      "end": 644.44,
      "text": "But the next time I tried to put over a fast one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.56,
      "end": 645.6,
      "text": "they'd stop me so"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.78,
      "end": 646.08,
      "text": "fast,"
    },
    {
      "start": 646.12,
      "end": 647.58,
      "text": "I'd swallow my teeth."
    },
    {
      "start": 648.62,
      "end": 649.14,
      "text": "Hell with that."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.4,
      "end": 652.44,
      "text": "You birds'll be in New York or Constantinople or"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.5,
      "end": 653.14,
      "text": "some place else."
    },
    {
      "start": 653.32,
      "end": 654.58,
      "text": "I'm in business here."
    },
    {
      "start": 655.46,
      "end": 655.82,
      "text": "\"But surely,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 656.04,
      "end": 656.66,
      "text": "Gutman began,"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.82,
      "end": 657.14,
      "text": "you can—\""
    },
    {
      "start": 657.38,
      "end": 658.74,
      "text": "\"I can't,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 658.76,
      "end": 659.56,
      "text": "Spade said"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.68,
      "end": 660.06,
      "text": "earnestly."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.28,
      "end": 661.52,
      "text": "I won't."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.06,
      "end": 662.66,
      "text": "I mean it."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.8,
      "end": 663.9,
      "text": "He sat up straight."
    },
    {
      "start": 664.14,
      "end": 666.52,
      "text": "A pleasant smile illuminated his face,"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.64,
      "end": 667.24,
      "text": "erasing its"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.34,
      "end": 668.16,
      "text": "dull lumpishness."
    },
    {
      "start": 668.94,
      "end": 670.82,
      "text": "He spoke rapidly in an agreeable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.88,
      "end": 671.8,
      "text": "persuasive tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 672.8,
      "end": 673.22,
      "text": "Listen to me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.26,
      "end": 673.56,
      "text": "Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.76,
      "end": 674.5,
      "text": "I'm telling"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.7,
      "end": 676.14,
      "text": "you what's best for all of us."
    },
    {
      "start": 676.32,
      "end": 678.4,
      "text": "If we don't give the police a fall-guy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.62,
      "end": 679.6,
      "text": "it's ten to one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.7,
      "end": 679.96,
      "text": "they'll"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.98,
      "end": 682.48,
      "text": "sooner or later stumble on information about the falcon."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.18,
      "end": 685.32,
      "text": "Then you'll have to duck for cover with it"
    },
    {
      "start": 685.42,
      "end": 686.72,
      "text": "no matter where you are,"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.5,
      "end": 689.98,
      "text": "and that's not going to help you make a fortune off it."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.7,
      "end": 691.38,
      "text": "Give them a fall"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.38,
      "end": 693.0,
      "text": "guy and they'll stop right there."
    },
    {
      "start": 693.7,
      "end": 694.3,
      "text": "\"Well, sir, that's just the point,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 694.3,
      "end": 694.54,
      "text": "sir,"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.72,
      "end": 695.84,
      "text": "that's just the point,"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.352,
      "end": 696.88,
      "text": "Gutman replied,"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.46,
      "end": 698.0,
      "text": "and still only"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.3,
      "end": 701.18,
      "text": "in his eyes was uneasiness faintly apparent."
    },
    {
      "start": 702.14,
      "end": 703.18,
      "text": "Will they stop right there?"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.86,
      "end": 704.5,
      "text": "Or won't the fall"
    },
    {
      "start": 704.6,
      "end": 707.3,
      "text": "guy be a fresh clue that as likely as not will"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.3,
      "end": 709.4,
      "text": "lead them to information about the falcon?"
    },
    {
      "start": 710.08,
      "end": 711.12,
      "text": "And on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.18,
      "end": 713.58,
      "text": "wouldn't you say they were stopped right now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.26,
      "end": 715.36,
      "text": "and that the best thing for us"
    },
    {
      "start": 715.36,
      "end": 716.86,
      "text": "to do is leave well enough alone?"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.86,
      "end": 720.7,
      "text": "A forked vein began to swell in Spade's forehead.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 721.04,
      "end": 721.14,
      "text": "Jesus,"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.92,
      "end": 722.12,
      "text": "you"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.32,
      "end": 723.66,
      "text": "don't know what it's all about either,"
    },
    {
      "start": 723.84,
      "end": 725.34,
      "text": "he said in a restrained tone."
    },
    {
      "start": 726.12,
      "end": 726.76,
      "text": "They're not asleep,"
    },
    {
      "start": 727.02,
      "end": 727.38,
      "text": "Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.56,
      "end": 728.7,
      "text": "They're lying low,"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.94,
      "end": 729.28,
      "text": "waiting."
    },
    {
      "start": 730.24,
      "end": 731.12,
      "text": "Try to get that."
    },
    {
      "start": 731.904,
      "end": 733.86,
      "text": "I'm in it up to my neck and they know it."
    },
    {
      "start": 734.4,
      "end": 737.05,
      "text": "That's all right as long as I do something when the time comes."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.76,
      "end": 739.32,
      "text": "But it won't be all right if I don't."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.96,
      "end": 741.52,
      "text": "His voice became persuasive again."
    },
    {
      "start": 742.2,
      "end": 742.5,
      "text": "Listen,"
    },
    {
      "start": 742.6,
      "end": 742.9,
      "text": "Gutman,"
    },
    {
      "start": 743.06,
      "end": 745.36,
      "text": "we've absolutely got to give them a victim."
    }
  ],
  "corrected": "claude"
}